'''Spinner-pit''' was a gambling game that involved a rotating circular tabletop and several balls. The balls would land on a number (such as 21), a symbol (such as a flask) and a color (such as green). Participants had to guess all three. [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]], thanks to her use of [[The Force/Legends|the Force]], was skilled at spinner-pit.<ref name="MJ" />

